          "name": "Flames of Battle",
          "description": "This unit cannot be defeated by damage from Burn status effects. This unit is not affected by stun effects.\n\nWhenever this unit enters the battlefield, whether at the start of battle or from reinforcements, it will Endure the next damage that would defeat it with 1HP. Endure effects cannot stack.\n\nWhile this unit has the Burn status effect, this unit has:\n- Attack increased to 1.5x. This effect does not stack with Enrage skills.\n- 50% damage reduction from attacks."
        }
      },
