        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Fuel to the Flames",
          "description": "This unit and all enemies are granted the Burn status effect, then all burning non-Water enemies are stunned for 100TU. All of these effects are triggered when this unit begins on the battlefield at the very start of battle.\n\nWhenever this unit defeats a non-conjured unit on the battlefield with an attack, this unit gains Endure and a Poison Ward.\n\nPoison Ward prevents Poison from being applied once, then is removed. Poison Wards cannot stack."
